A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the Citizens Christian Academy girls softball team for winning the 2024
2 GIAA Class A State Softball Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Citizens Christian Academy girls softball team has established and
4 maintained a proud tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics;
5 and
6 WHEREAS, this superlative team completed another triumphant season of softball
7 competition by posting an outstanding record of 21 wins and only 5 losses; and
8 WHEREAS, excellent play, superior teamwork, and extraordinary resilience made this team
9 a spectacular one to observe throughout the season, and as a fitting finale to its remarkable
10 2024 campaign, the team claimed victory at the 2024 GIAA Class A State Softball
11 Championship; and
12 WHEREAS, junior Gracie Giddens, named the 2024 Class A Player of the Year, earned
13 Class A All-State and District 6 All-Region honors and achieved an exemplary .530 batting
14 average; and
